---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="CBS2 News | DenArt Media" description="DenArt body painting studio featured on CBS2 News">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-6 bg-deepest">
    <a href="/in_media/" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-gold hover:text-brand-gold-hover mb-8">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
      </svg>
      Back to Media
    </a>

    <article>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">CBS2 News</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-8">CBS | TV, United States</p>

      <div class="aspect-video mb-8 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-900">
        <iframe 
          src="https://newyork.cbslocal.com/video/4445457-unique-valentines-ideas/" 
          class="w-full h-full"
          frameborder="0" 
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p>This year's Valentine's Day, we were honored and fortunate to have our Paint in the Dark UV class for couples featured on CBS2's segment on Unique Valentine's Ideas.</p>
        <p>CBS2's Vanessa Murdock came to our studio in Williamsburg, Brooklyn, few days before Valentine's Day for a private demo and interviewed our founder Danny Setiawan.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
